highlights.text: ATLXS has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “PASSO BEM SOLTO - Slowed” is the highest at #16.
“PASSO BEM SOLTO - Super Slowed” by ATLXS is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #89.
“blue” by yung kai has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 200 days straight.
“Giữ Mãi Nụ Cười” by Huy Dean is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 34 spots at #48.
